snippet.title: Making a handheld game with no game engine in 7 days
snippet.description:
I spent 1 week making a quirky tennis game for the Playdate!

Get the game here!: https://squidgod.itch.io/almost-tennis
Get the source code and supporting the channel!: https://www.patreon.com/squidgoddev

Follow me on Twitter to see sneak peaks/updates!: https://twitter.com/SquidGodDev
Join my Discord!: https://discord.gg/kDM8RU4aFt

Music/SFX from Epidemic Sound. Get a 30 day free trial: https://share.epidemicsound.com/njknzw
